{"url": "https://web.archive.org/web/20150311184400/http://conservative-headlines.com:80/2015/03/south-african-firm-ordered-to-lay-off-3389-white-employees", "text": "A South African utility company has been given an ultimatum to reduce it\u2019s number of white employees by 44.3% over the next five years. This means 3,389 whites have to go. It is part of the Federal \u201cBlack Empowerment\u201d program.\n\nFor years, Eskom has been under orders to only hire non-whites as new employees. The firm says it is having major problems finding enough qualified non-white applicants. Currently, Eskom\u2019s middle managers are 30% white and it\u2019s skilled labor force is 21% white.\n\nThe South African government has also ordered Eskom to reduce it\u2019s safety requirements to make it easier for non-white applicants to qualify for jobs.\n\nEskom is ordered to reduce the number of white engineers by 1,081, and the number of white skilled laborers by 2,179.\n\nSouth Africa is currently experiencing a rapid collapse of it\u2019s electrical infrastructure and power routinely goes out all over the country.\n\nSource (South Africa Channel 24)", "images": ["https://web.archive.org/web/20150311184400im_/http://conservative-headlines.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/no_background_cofcc.gif", "https://web.archive.org/web/20150311184400im_/http://i2.wp.com/conservative-headlines.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/SCE.jpg?resize=150%2C150", "https://web.archive.org/web/20150311184400im_/http://i2.wp.com/conservative-headlines.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/stop_rape_by_cloud_a_day_stock-d4aya5m1.jpg?resize=150%2C150", "https://web.archive.org/web/20150311184400im_/http://i1.wp.com/conservative-headlines.com/wp-content/uploads/2009/01/Southafricanhomelandsmap.png?resize=150%2C150", "https://web.archive.org/web/20150311184400im_/http://conservative-headlines.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/Raven_Patches.jpg", "https://web.archive.org/web/20150311184400im_/http://i1.wp.com/conservative-headlin